  "texts": [
    "Instead of building prompt-specific models, their work introduced a rubricspecific model.",
    "Prompt-specific models tends to overlook various attributes that are integral to the rubrics.",
    "Rubrics provide criteria to be considered during the grading of students' essay.",
    "Rubric-specific training models demonstrated the ability to capture features from essays that are shared across different prompts.",
    "Attributes such as the student's grade level serve as important indicators in scoring essays, enabling adjustments based on the writing ability within the same grade level."
  ],
